						<p class="describe"><c:out value="${recommend.md_text}"/></p>
						<p class="run-time"> 런타임: <c:out value="${recommend.md_runtime}"/>’    .     <span>심의등급: <c:out value="${recommend.md_grade}"/> </span></p>
